              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "The mechanism this JIRA proposed would make most sense for features specific to a single scheduler.  As queue-moving functionality is probably something that the Capacity Scheduler would like at some point as well, I think it would make more sense to directly add it as a ResourceManager API.",
